{"id": 1380, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些征兆出现，老板可能不要你了？", "description": "这心酸，堪比一场小型失恋。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 2451, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170322111733WO4X5l3QUrE6jPdB.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-12-16T03:00:05Z", "options": [{"id": 144902, "content": "怀孕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870045}, {"id": 144905, "content": "看着你对你叹气，然后转过身就走了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871253}, {"id": 145418, "content": "公司要培养人才", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 873002}, {"id": 156426, "content": "动不动就怼你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875168}, {"id": 154635, "content": "我觉得你是一个聪明人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906731}, {"id": 155403, "content": "我一直挺欣赏你的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908719}, {"id": 147469, "content": "每次老板单独开会，核心人员都没有你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 344852}, {"id": 151824, "content": "不理我了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896848}, {"id": 160784, "content": "说了干的不错，脸上却不符合话语的表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796044}, {"id": 146450, "content": "不直接跟你对话，让身边红人来穿花啊，说你哪里哪里要改善。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 877399}, {"id": 147218, "content": "冷落你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879307}, {"id": 147745, "content": "反正就是有意无意忽略你，向别人咨询与你有关的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 880794}, {"id": 145698, "content": "不搭理你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724971}, {"id": 144679, "content": "每天微信少于100条", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863356}, {"id": 144938, "content": "你先……这个不急", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188019}, {"id": 144685, "content": "跟你说：你还是做别的吧…", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869727}, {"id": 144688, "content": "老找茬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720099}, {"id": 144690, "content": "什么也不教给你做，把你放到一边不理你", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847918}, {"id": 144691, "content": "当你打开这个话题的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074652}, {"id": 145459, "content": "老板让你离开现在岗位，较长时间去负责一两项临时性的工作。并且一直未有招回原岗的动作。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871226}, {"id": 144692, "content": "不打电话催你上班了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867033}, {"id": 144693, "content": "第一句是：哦，第二句是： 啊，第三句是： 你还是有吧------(电影喜剧之王)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869792}, {"id": 145973, "content": "呵呵 转身走了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875536}, {"id": 144694, "content": "哎，小王，你把地扫扫吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666515}, {"id": 144950, "content": "在看让谁负责的时候 看到你却点了别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 871383}, {"id": 144695, "content": "让我拿工卡和ta下去一趟。。。(亲身经历)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569128}, {"id": 144696, "content": "没有找你交流的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863524}, {"id": 144697, "content": "此处不留爷，自有留爷处", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800987}, {"id": 144699, "content": "每次都会跟你说，你是一个有希望的孩子，然而……没有什么工作给你做", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869829}, {"id": 144701, "content": "以后再说", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838688}, {"id": 144702, "content": "无视你的存在", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869849}, {"id": 144703, "content": "无视你的存在", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869849}, {"id": 144704, "content": "对你的提议，左耳进右耳出了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 864477}, {"id": 144705, "content": "直接明说 再这样 会解雇", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 860438}, {"id": 144707, "content": "像给丫炒了！想爆抽杂种操的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260866}, {"id": 152899, "content": "即将工作的我感觉很惶恐啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902280}, {"id": 144708, "content": "我不care 你感受", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808649}, {"id": 144709, "content": "作为学生，对你们表示同情???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712408}, {"id": 150853, "content": "我是反过来，谁跟我玩的好，老板就开除谁，他是不是在变着法子要我走？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 582058}, {"id": 144711, "content": "你说，连选个图都选不好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 783523}, {"id": 144712, "content": "把你比别人做的好的工作定一个标准来统一规划，然后这标准还远低于你力所能及的高度", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869931}, {"id": 149576, "content": "无视，边缘化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 885726}, {"id": 144715, "content": "从来都是我炒老板鱿鱼", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 823867}, {"id": 144716, "content": "明明看你不爽还不批评你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805902}, {"id": 144717, "content": "不造啊，没被炒过", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 812943}, {"id": 144718, "content": "从不回复你邮件开始", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610147}, {"id": 144719, "content": "不搭理你了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 856815}, {"id": 150607, "content": "国企职工路过，没这种可能", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890612}, {"id": 144721, "content": "把你的存在感用各种方式逐渐抹消", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 710847}, {"id": 151633, "content": "把你当空气～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 894487}]}